OL,5, The boss of the rail operator that runs
OL,6, Avanti West Coast and Transpennine     
OL,7, Express has apologised for the         
OL,8, disruption to services experienced by  
OL,9, passengers in recent months.           
OL,11,FSteve Montgomery, managing director of 
OL,12,FFirst Rail, told the BBC the issues had
OL,13,Fbeen caused by a backlog of driver     
OL,14,Ftraining during the pandemic.          
OL,16,FHe said that because of sickness levels
OL,17,Fand drivers not working overtime, the  
OL,18,Fcompany was not able to fill the gaps. 
OL,20,F"We apologise to customers," he said.  
